#Title pan example

#Tempo 96

@1 sawtooth gain 127

A @1 v5 o4

A p0 c2 r p64 c2 r p128 c2
A r1

A px-64 c2 r px0 c2 r px+64 c2
A r1

; Pan can be changed in the middle of a note if the note is slurred into a pan command.
A px0 c3 & px-40 w3 px+40 r3
A r1

; Complex mid-note pan change that changes the pan in discrete steps.
A p0 a & [ w4 p+16 ]8 w4 [ w4 p-16 ]8 r4

